snippet.title: SHADOWS OF KEPLER - GAMEPLAY
snippet.description:
Download the demo on Steam. If you like the game, support us on Kickstarter to make this game a reality.

Play the Demo (PC Steam): https://store.steampowered.com/app/1121510/Shadows_of_Kepler/
Pre-order and support on Kickstarter: https://kickstarter.com/projects/shadowsofkepler/shadows-of-kepler-the-game
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Shadows-of-Kepler-320174495593474
Homepage: https://www.shadowsofkepler.com
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/shadowsofkepler/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/HoleInfinite
